"Social media activity regarding the #putinmissing event centers on speculation about Vladimir Putin's whereabouts, with users questioning his location and status. Conflicting timeline details have emerged from unverified sources, including a security briefing citing a disputed 73:15 timestamp linked to a private police bulletin. Other reports suggest an intercepted radio update and a named suspect transfer occurred prior to the first official briefing. Additionally, one post claims to show Putin, attempting to resolve the uncertainty."